    <string name="how_to_use_title">How to Use</string>
    <string name="how_to_use_message">Always fill your tank to the MAXIMUM level before recording a fill-up.\n\n1. First fill-up: Enter your current odometer reading and the fuel you added. This is your starting point — no consumption is shown yet.\n\n2. Drive until your next fill-up.\n\n3. Fill to the MAX level again. Enter the new odometer reading and the exact amount of fuel added. The app calculates your consumption from the distance driven and fuel used.\n\nTip: For best accuracy, always fill to the same level each time.</string>
